      <td>Journal Jekyll Theme</td>
      <td>Jekyll Themes</td>
      <td>Yes</td>
      <td>$49</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>And footnotes<sup id="fnref:1" role="doc-noteref"><a href="#fn:1" class="footnote" rel="footnote">1</a></sup>, which link to explanations<sup id="fnref:2" role="doc-noteref"><a href="#fn:2" class="footnote" rel="footnote">2</a></sup> at the bottom of the page<sup id="fnref:3" role="doc-noteref"><a href="#fn:3" class="footnote" rel="footnote">3</a></sup>.</p>

